{"tid":1230992,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"x你老母，你個良心去左邊，個腦係咪裝屎","createTime":"2019-06-16T11:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T11:03:51.000Z","uid":123804,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"89ea4b781f3b95eec437138f7dc0f7f17fb492dc","tid":1230992,"uid":123804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T11:03:51.000Z","msg":"其實已經有人死左 就不應該再講啲咩<br />\n包括有冇收錢 消防員救援既事<br />\n無論佢因咩事而選擇輕生 <br />\n佢都走左 俾人安息啦<br />\n我都知香港好多人因為呢件事好難受 心情好沉重<br />\n呢件事最難過既一定係佢既屋企人同救援人員<br />\n消防員都盡左力 佢地救不到 望住個人係自己眼前跌落去 一定好難受<br />\n大家都香港人 好心積下口德<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">輿論壓力真係可以殺死一個人架</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">R.I.P</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">願你如麥子 歸去那一片你愛的田</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CkUxyUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCkUxyUk.png&h=a3e0833d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xBPNnNG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxBPNnNG.png&h=6ea77a12&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wQgzNen.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwQgzNen.png&h=603c8536&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KzFMDk3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKzFMDk3.png&h=26aec0bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OrhnV7L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOrhnV7L.png&h=49321d70&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dhmTik9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdhmTik9.png&h=fe7e0e12&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}